---
description: Auto-triggers code-quality-guard skill when lint, pre-commit, or CI security config changes.
globs: biome.json, .biomeignore, .husky/pre-commit, .github/workflows/**/*.yml, .gitleaks.toml, .semgrepignore
alwaysApply: false
---

When any matching file is created or modified, read and follow the code-quality-guard skill:
- Skill file: `agent-os/skills/code-quality-guard/SKILL.md`
- Verify the 3-layer quality pipeline: Biome (lint + format), Husky pre-commit hooks, CI security scanning
- Ensure lint-staged config in package.json matches the pre-commit hook
- Validate CI workflows include all security checks (Gitleaks, Semgrep, audit)
